def removePuncStr(s):
    for c in string.punctuation:
        s = s.replace(c," ")
    return s.lower()

def stopText(text_array):
    stop_words = list(stopwords.words('english'))
    #+["phone","phones","iphone","iphones","apple"]
    stopped_text = []
    
    words = word_tokenize(text_array)
    h2 = ''
    for w in words:
        if w.lower() not in stop_words and len(w)>3:
            h2 = h2 + ' ' + w
    stopped_text.append(h2)
    return stopped_text[0]
    
def removeNumbersStr(s):
    for c in range(10):
        n = str(c)
        s = s.replace(n," ")
    return s

# getting word embeddings for each word - glove

def get_coefs(word, *arr): 
    return word, np.asarray(arr, dtype='float32')
embeddings_index = dict(get_coefs(*o.rstrip().rsplit(' ')) for o in open("glove.6B.300d.txt",encoding='utf-8'))

In [29]:
vector_df = pd.DataFrame(columns = ["Vector"+str(i) for i in range(300)])

for row in range(0,len(df_apple)):
    
    for i in comprehend.detect_syntax(Text=df_apple["clean_text"][row], LanguageCode='en')["SyntaxTokens"]:
        if i["PartOfSpeech"]["Tag"] == "NOUN" and i["PartOfSpeech"]["Score"] > 0.6:
            word = i["Text"]
            try:
                if word not in vector_df.index:
                    a_series = pd.Series(embeddings_index[word],index= vector_df.columns,name= word)
                    vector_df = vector_df.append(a_series)
            except:
                pass

# cosine similarity

def cosine(v1, v2):
    if norm(v1) > 0 and norm(v2) > 0:
        return dot(v1, v2) / (norm(v1) * norm(v2))
    else:
        return 0.0
In [40]:
threshold_similarity = 0.5
def map_the_similarity(text_array):
    max_sim = -1
    best_feature =""
    list_of_best_features = []
    for feature in Features:
        for word in text_array:
            
            try: 
                sim = cosine(embeddings_index[word],embeddings_index[feature.lower()])
                #print (word,sim,feature)
                if sim > max_sim:
                    max_sim =sim
                    best_feature = feature
                if sim>threshold_similarity:
                    list_of_best_features.append(feature)
            except:
                pass
    list_of_best_features.append(best_feature)
    return list(set(list_of_best_features))

words_to_ignore = ["phone","phones","iphone","iphones","apple","device","product","ios"]

for row in range(0,len(df_apple)):
    all_words = []
    for i in comprehend.detect_syntax(Text=df_apple["clean_text"][row], LanguageCode='en')["SyntaxTokens"]:
        if i["PartOfSpeech"]["Tag"] == "NOUN" and i["PartOfSpeech"]["Score"] > 0.7:
            if i["Text"] not in words_to_ignore:
                all_words.append(i["Text"])
    
    best_features = map_the_similarity(all_words)
    #print (best_features)
    df_apple.loc[row,"feature"] = best_features
